data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home with a Study! Neutral colors and ceiling fans throughout.  Living room has a wood-burning fireplace. 2 Eating areas, a Formal Dining Room, and Breakfast Nook with a nice-sized pantry. Kitchen w/ Flat-top Stove, Microwave, and Dishwasher. Master Bedroom has a walk-in closet and a large master bath w/ custom vanities. All Tile floors downstairs and carpets upstairs. Large enclosed covered Patio great for entertaining. Fenced yard with mature trees. Close to Shopping, 1604, 410. Northside schools.
